{"tid":275387,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運房局：研究輕鐵路軌及馬路分開　料需5至10年","createTime":"2017-06-08T03:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T14:27:29.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"666fa1fe31553df08dd0fa1b962521d22d976715","tid":275387,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T03:58:49.000Z","msg":"政府昨公布最新《公共交通策略研究》，就8項主要公共交通提出67項措施，其中提出重組輕鐵路線，長遠需研究在新界西北興建新鐵路接駁市區的可行性。對於人、車及輕鐵爭路的問題，運輸及房屋局表示，將研究如何將路軌與馬路分開，但改道問題大費周章，估計需要5至10年時間。<br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局副秘書長陳帥夫在商台節目表示，就着輕鐵問題，政府報告在短中長期都有答案，局方將全面深入研究可否「飛天遁地」，即鐵路跟路面分開，但要改道必定會大費周章，相信至少要5至10年時間。<br />\n<br />\n陳帥夫又說，當局會研究興建一條新重鐵，由新界直接出市區，希望能效法港島北，「重鐵在地下疏導，輕鐵上面繼續行駛」。"},{"pid":"24a6be5f228f4837246a9db2681345b4a05a98d3","tid":275387,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T03:59:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170608/s00001/1496887231560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170608%2Fs00001%2F1496887231560&d=al3u4Y9mZyU%2BqV7qNFCnKxFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=d9b0f0d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170608%2Fs00001%2F1496887231560&h=1cdfc7f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170608/s00001/1496887231560</a>"},{"pid":"e1e89b72ac9b21f48c78742d2881b2a5e84558ae","tid":275387,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea2098efd65aee1310f0cdb9daf205fbc41facd","tid":275387,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:02:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab6e793158a30fa8a14efc00e3d701e9aacb13a7","tid":275387,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實西